{"tid":1525602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應承我，點都唔好殺黑警","createTime":"2019-09-01T01:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T02:08:04.000Z","uid":97181,"like":31,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"de891d6364838bc7973b605308225ecad9838216","tid":1525602,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"贏咗之後，都唔好殺黑警<br />\n用返非致命武力懲罰呢班黑警<br />\n<br />\n1. 半開放空間狂射催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 用警棍狂毆頭部頸部<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 橡膠子彈直射頭部<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 布袋彈直射頭部<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n懲罰完仲要去轉新屋嶺打到四肢骨折<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再等返十個八個鐘先送院<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果捱唔住死咗即係身子弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔關武力級別事架<br />\n急不及待好想玩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔留返條命就睇唔到呢一日架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"616a5c19259a93864217483a6f4acc3ec613e596","tid":1525602,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:49:48.000Z","msg":"831恐襲同721恐襲冇分別<br />\n我正式宣佈香港警察係有牌黑社會兼恐怖分子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeYzNsiOy00o&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=f339f903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r2_c1Lc6MiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr2_c1Lc6MiU&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=d0e139cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r2_c1Lc6MiU</a>"},{"pid":"cef1b9fc30d7149515100f5b1411b877216f429c","tid":1525602,"uid":50275,"like":1,"dislike":0